
eSim installation instructions
=================================

Table of contents

    1. eSim installation in Ubuntu OS

    2. eSim Uninstallation in Ubuntu OS

    3. Manual Package Download (If Automated Download Fails)


1. eSim installation in Ubuntu OS

    i.  Download and Extract eSim - After downloading eSim-2.3.zip, extract it using:

            $ unzip eSim-2.3.zip

    ii. Navigate to the eSim Directory - Change into the top-level eSim directory:

            $ cd eSim-2.3
    
    iii. Run the Installer - To install eSim and required tools, run:

            $ python3 main.py

    This will guide you through the installation and setup of tools like Ngspice, KiCad, GHDL, and Verilator.


2. eSim Uninstallation in Ubuntu OS
     
    To uninstall eSim and its components, run the same script:

            $ python3 main.py

3. Manual Package Download (If Automated Download Fails)

    If downloading packages fails during installation, you can manually download them using the links below. 
    After downloading, save each file using the exact name shown in the brackets, including the .tar.gz extension, and place them into the following folder:

    eSim-2.3/nghdl/packages/

    Download Links
    Saved Filename	        Download Link
    ghdl-nightly.tar.gz	        https://github.com/ghdl/ghdl/archive/refs/tags/nightly.tar.gz
    ghdl-4.1.0.tar.gz	        https://github.com/ghdl/ghdl/archive/refs/tags/v4.1.0.tar.gz
    ghdl-4.0.0.tar.gz	        https://github.com/ghdl/ghdl/archive/refs/tags/v4.0.0.tar.gz
    ghdl-3.0.0.tar.gz	        https://github.com/ghdl/ghdl/archive/refs/tags/v3.0.0.tar.gz
    verilator-4.228.tar.gz	https://github.com/verilator/verilator/archive/refs/tags/v4.228.tar.gz
    verilator-5.020.tar.gz	https://github.com/verilator/verilator/archive/refs/tags/v5.020.tar.gz
    verilator-5.026.tar.gz	https://github.com/verilator/verilator/archive/refs/tags/v5.026.tar.gz
    verilator-5.030.tar.gz	https://github.com/verilator/verilator/archive/refs/tags/v5.030.tar.gz
    ngspice-38.tar.gz	        https://github.com/imr/ngspice/archive/refs/tags/ngspice-38.tar.gz
    ngspice-40.tar.gz	        https://github.com/imr/ngspice/archive/refs/tags/ngspice-40.tar.gz
    ngspice-43.tar.gz	        https://github.com/imr/ngspice/archive/refs/tags/ngspice-43.tar.gz

Important: Make sure each file is saved exactly as listed (e.g., ghdl-4.1.0.tar.gz) before placing it in the nghdl/packages/ directory.
